==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
A quote from the [[wikipedia:Analects_of_Confucius|Analects of Confucius]].  When [[wikipedia:Confucius|Confucius]] was in [[wikipedia:Qi_%28state%29|Qi]], he heard the [[韶|Shao]] music, and for three months he did not know the taste of meat.  He said, "I never knew music could reach this level of excellence!"

Literally: Did not know the taste of meat for three months.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: sān yuè bù zhī ròu wèi

===Idiom===
'''三月不知肉味'''

# Describes a situation in which one is totally captivated by whatever activity is taking place.

#: ''[[有]][[人]][[认为]][[wikipedia:Bei_Dao|北岛]][[在]][[这]][[本]][[书]][[中]][[没有]][[表现]][[出]][[思想]][[之]][[美]]，[[但]][[那]][[是]][[评论家]][[的]][[事]]，[[对于]][[我等]][[普通]][[读者]][[来]][[说]]，[[这样]][[的]][[文字]]，[[已经]][[足以]]'''三月不知肉味'''[[了]]。.'' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

#: ''[[有]][[人]][[認為]][[wikipedia:Bei_Dao|北島]][[在]][[這]][[本]][[書]][[中]][[沒有]][[表現]][[出]][[思想]][[之]][[美]]，[[但]][[那]][[是]][[評論家]][[的]][[事]]，[[對於]][[我等]][[普通]][[讀者]][[來]][[說]]，[[這樣]][[的]][[文字]]，[[已經]][[足以]]'''三月不知肉味'''[[了]]。.'' ([[Traditional Chinese]])

